<seg id=1> The South Korean military continuously having accidents, the opposition calls on resignation of the defense minister </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Seoul, Reuters. The South Korean opposition party called on the resignation of the defense minister Cheon Yong Taek yesterday, for a number of military accidents days before, including firing missile and candle bomb to civilian residential area. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> According a Korean official, the newest story was that, error took place in a military exercise held at the dawn of yesterday. A candle bomb hit and passed two walls of of an old woman's home. </seg>
<seg id=4> The old woman's home is near to the landing site of the fragments of the missile explosion two days ago. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=5> Navy official said that the candle bomb lanched by the Korean marines went much farther than expected and landed on the civilian house in Kimp0. </seg>
<seg id=6> Kimpo is west to Seoul. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=7> The opposition Grand National Party issued a statement, saying "defense minister Cheon Yong Taek should resign immediately, or (President Kim Daejun) should remove him from his position. </seg>
<seg id=8> A government not afraid of the people is not the people's government." </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=9> The statement said, "Cheon Yong Taek tries to save his position, and only gives his apology..., this is too big for his boots." </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=10> The defense ministry apologized for the missile accident the day before yesterday. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=11> Navy officials said, the shell of the candle bomb hit over two walls and entered the shower room. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=12> He said that the 83 year old woman was over scared and now is in hospital for treatment. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=13> Last Friday, Korean military accidentally lanched a ground-to-air missile, which exploded in the air and injured at least 3 civilians. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=14> Official from the defense ministry said that the missile was accidentally launched when the military technical personnel was checking up the weapons at the air base in the western port city Inchon. </seg>
<seg id=15> Inchon is 40 kilometers away from the border of the two Koreas. </seg>
</p>
